00:19:07.020 --> 00:19:08.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Está preparado?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Não.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:19:09.690 --> 00:19:11.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mas pode abrir as portas.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:19:21.827 --> 00:19:24.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Callum, quero falar com você sobre a vida.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:19:25.247 --> 00:19:26.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>E sobre crescer.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:19:26.832 --> 00:19:29.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>E sobre como há mudanças...</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:19:29.251 --> 00:19:30.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>que não se esperava.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:19:37.301 --> 00:19:40.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tentei ser altruísta enquanto rei,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>mas, como pai,</i></c.bg_transparent>

219
00:19:41.513 --> 00:19:42.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>tenho um desejo egoísta,</i></c.bg_transparent>

220
00:19:44.099 --> 00:19:47.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>e é que você e Ezran... sejam livres.</i></c.bg_transparent>

221
00:19:48.729 --> 00:19:50.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Rejeite as correntes da história.</i></c.bg_transparent>

222
00:19:50.772 --> 00:19:53.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Não deixe o passado definir seu futuro,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>como fiz.</i></c.bg_transparent>

223
00:19:54.484 --> 00:19:56.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Liberte-se do seu passado!</i></c.bg_transparent>

224
00:19:56.987 --> 00:19:59.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aprenda com ele, entenda-o</i></c.bg_transparent>

225
00:19:59.448 --> 00:20:00.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>e o deixe ir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

226
00:20:00.782 --> 00:20:05.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Crie um futuro melhor vindo</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>do seu próprio coração e imaginação.</i></c.bg_transparent>

227
00:20:08.790 --> 00:20:11.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sinto muito por nunca tê-las conhecido.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:20:12.252 --> 00:20:13.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Suas mães.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:20:14.129 --> 00:20:16.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Obrigada por contar a história,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Lorde Viren.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:20:17.049 --> 00:20:20.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tenho sorte em ter escutado</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tantas histórias lindas.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:20:20.260 --> 00:20:22.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Foi assim que eu as conheci.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:20:22.471 --> 00:20:26.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Elas eram muito corajosas,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>fortes e sábias.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:20:26.975 --> 00:20:29.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não tenho nada a ver com isso,</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:20:29.436 --> 00:20:31.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>mas sei que estariam orgulhosas de você!</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:20:40.405 --> 00:20:43.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Parece estranho</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sentir falta de quem nunca conheci...</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:20:43.784 --> 00:20:45.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>mas sinto muita falta delas.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:20:46.787 --> 00:20:49.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rainha Aanya, sabendo disso agora,</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:20:49.748 --> 00:20:53.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>entende por que acredito que,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>se elas estivessem aqui hoje,</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:20:54.002 --> 00:20:55.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>escolheriam se unir a nós</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:20:55.963 --> 00:20:57.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>e lutar ao nosso lado?</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:20:58.548 --> 00:20:59.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Acho que tem razão.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:21:00.259 --> 00:21:01.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Talvez escolhessem.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:21:03.720 --> 00:21:07.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Mas eu... não escolherei.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-O quê?</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:21:08.183 --> 00:21:11.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Devemos muito a Katolis. Não há dúvidas.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:21:12.229 --> 00:21:14.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Recebemos tanta bondade</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:21:14.564 --> 00:21:16.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>e coragem e sacrifício.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:21:17.192 --> 00:21:21.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mas não posso pagar a dívida</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de cem mil vidas salvas</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:21:22.281 --> 00:21:25.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>mandando um milhão de homens</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e mulheres para morrer.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:21:25.867 --> 00:21:28.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Você não ouviu? Você não...</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:21:29.371 --> 00:21:30.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rei Ahling!</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:21:31.123 --> 00:21:33.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ajude-me a fazê-la entender.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:21:33.834 --> 00:21:38.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Viren, nós simpatizamos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>com o drama de Katolis, mas...</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:21:38.630 --> 00:21:41.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-sinto que não podemos mais...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Covarde!</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:21:42.718 --> 00:21:43.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Traidores!</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:21:44.094 --> 00:21:47.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cada um de vocês aqui hoje</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:21:47.597 --> 00:21:50.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>traiu a humanidade!</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:21:50.809 --> 00:21:53.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lorde Viren, sinto muito, mas...</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:21:55.188 --> 00:21:58.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Guarde suas desculpas vazias.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:21:59.735 --> 00:22:01.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O perigo é iminente!</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:22:01.194 --> 00:22:03.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chegarão ao nosso lado da fronteira.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:22:03.238 --> 00:22:07.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todos pagarão o preço</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por ignorar meus avisos!</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:22:12.122 --> 00:22:16.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>E, finalmente, deve se perguntar</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>sobre o segredo que prometi contar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

263
00:22:16.918 --> 00:22:18.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Bem, boas notícias,</i></c.bg_transparent>

264
00:22:18.503 --> 00:22:22.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>o segredo está escondido</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>no chalé de Banther, onde está agora!</i></c.bg_transparent>

265
00:22:22.924 --> 00:22:24.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Não planejei bem?</i></c.bg_transparent>

266
00:22:24.843 --> 00:22:27.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que bom que estamos no chalé de Banther.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:22:28.722 --> 00:22:31.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Agora, suba as escadas à sala de jogos.</i></c.bg_transparent>

268
00:22:31.350 --> 00:22:33.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Lá, escondi um cubo incomum</i></c.bg_transparent>

269
00:22:33.435 --> 00:22:35.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>com runas em cada lado.</i></c.bg_transparent>

270
00:22:40.442 --> 00:22:44.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Esse cubo é uma relíquia antiga</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>que foi passada por eras.</i></c.bg_transparent>

271
00:22:44.780 --> 00:22:47.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pertenceu a um mago elfo em Xadia,</i></c.bg_transparent>

272
00:22:47.491 --> 00:22:49.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>o arquimago Aaravos,</i></c.bg_transparent>

273
00:22:49.409 --> 00:22:52.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>um mestre de todas</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>as seis fontes primárias.</i></c.bg_transparent>

274
00:22:53.121 --> 00:22:57.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Está escondido numa caixa de chaves, pois</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>é conhecido como a "Chave de Aaravos",</i></c.bg_transparent>

275
00:22:58.126 --> 00:23:01.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>e a lenda diz que ele destranca algo</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>de grande poder em Xadia.</i></c.bg_transparent>

276
00:23:02.798 --> 00:23:06.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Talvez seja você, Callum,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>que descobrirá os segredos da chave.</i></c.bg_transparent>

277
00:23:09.179 --> 00:23:12.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>E um último segredo-bônus-super-secreto:</i></c.bg_transparent>

278
00:23:12.974 --> 00:23:15.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sabia que Isca, nosso amigo mais ácido,</i></c.bg_transparent>

279
00:23:15.852 --> 00:23:18.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>secretamente ama carinho na barriga?</i></c.bg_transparent>

280
00:23:22.150 --> 00:23:25.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quem é o rabugento mais gordinho?</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:23:29.282 --> 00:23:32.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pensou que eu era só</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>um velho capitão do mar,</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:23:32.244 --> 00:23:33.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>mas também sou sábio.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:23:33.787 --> 00:23:36.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Admito. Você é bem sábio mesmo.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:23:37.666 --> 00:23:40.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quer saber o outro segredo da vida?</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:23:41.420 --> 00:23:42.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Meias à prova d'água!</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:23:42.921 --> 00:23:45.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É uma metáfora. Pense nisso.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:23:46.967 --> 00:23:48.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Você só me mostrou as meias.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:23:48.760 --> 00:23:50.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isso não é uma metáfora!</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:24:04.734 --> 00:24:05.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por que isso?</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:24:06.695 --> 00:24:09.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Você é meu irmão</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>e significa tudo para mim.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:24:09.406 --> 00:24:10.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>É uma pegadinha?</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:24:11.616 --> 00:24:12.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Não, eu só te amo.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:24:13.118 --> 00:24:14.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bem, eu também te amo.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:24:15.871 --> 00:24:18.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Já chegamos lá? Estamos perto?</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:24:20.083 --> 00:24:21.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estamos chegando.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:24:22.169 --> 00:24:23.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cheiro de terra!</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:24:32.137 --> 00:24:34.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O que foi isso? Uma sombra?</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:24:34.639 --> 00:24:36.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perguntou ao pirata errado.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:24:37.476 --> 00:24:39.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tem algo lá em cima.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:25:23.855 --> 00:25:25.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Legendas: Lenise Fernandes</c.bg_transparent>

